# Sanctuary Home Feed Spec (mandatory)

Before editing matching files, **read** `docs/SANCTUARY_HOME_FEED_SPEC.md` and treat it as the source of truth for `/my-sanctuary`.

## Hard constraints

- **No regressions** ‚Äî preserve `MySanctuaryHomeServer` auth, session cookies, and existing hooks (`useFeed`, `useSanctuaryStories`, `useAuth`).
- **Hybrid merge** ‚Äî real Supabase payloads from `home-data.ts` + demo personas from `demo-personas.ts` via `buildMergedHomeFeed`.
- **No dead UI** ‚Äî tray live ‚Üí `/stream/[id]`; story ring ‚Üí `StoryModalViewer`; video ‚Üí `/parables/[id]`; heart ‚Üí `post_likes`; Get Pass ‚Üí `sanctuary_event_registrations`.
- **Do not** paste broken mock URLs (`https://unsplash.com` bare links) or duplicate simulation user lists outside `demo-personas.ts`.

## Database mapping

| Spec | Production |
|------|------------|
| `sanctuary_posts` | `public.posts` |
| `sanctuary_live_streams` | `public.profiles` where `is_live` |
| `sanctuary_events` | `public.sanctuary_events` (optional SQL) |
| `sanctuary_event_registrations` | `public.sanctuary_event_registrations` |

